get.description:
Use the query parameter "fulfilled" to filter your responses by Bulk Order Requests that have been fulfilled or not.

Use the page and page_size parameters to control the pagination. Set page_size=0 to return all objects.

The fields included are defined as follows:

    {
        "id": "12345678-abcd-1234-abcd-1234567890ab",  // the root order id
        "created": "2024-05-11T12:00:00.000000Z",  // The date & time the order was created
        "updated": "2024-05-11T12:00:00.000000Z",  // The date & time the order was last updated
        "order_number": "240123",  // The Bulk Order number shown on the Tenovi Web App
        "shipping_name": "First Last",
        "shipping_address": "123 Tenovi St",
        "shipping_city": "Portsmouth",
        "shipping_state": "NH",
        "shipping_zip_code": "12345",
        "shipping_status": "Pending",
            // Readable order status: Requested, Client Action Required, Pending, Shipped, or Delivered
        "shipping_tracking_link": "https://tenovi.com",  // The tracking link, if the order has shipped,
        "fulfilled": True,
        "requested_by": "jdoe@tenovi.com",  // The user that requested this order
        "shipped_on": "2024-05-11T12:00:00.000000Z",
        "delivered_on": "2024-05-18T12:00:00.000000Z",
        "notify_emails": "jdoe@tenovi.com,rsmith@tenovi.com",
        "contents": [
            {
                "name": "Tenovi BPM - L",  // The name of the included device/supply item
                "quantity: 10,  // The quantity
                "kit_id": 0,  // The Kit ID. 0 indicates the item was shipped separately. Items with a matching
                              // kit_id > 0 were kitted together by Tenovi
            },
            ...
        ]
        "manifest": [
            {
                "order_section": "Loose Items",
                "kitted_items": [],
                "loose_items": [
                    {
                        "imei": "123123123123123",
                        "device_type": "Tenovi Cellular Pulse Ox"
                    },
                    ...
                ]
            },
            {
                "order_section": "Kit 1",
                "kitted_items": [
                    {
                        "kit_number": 0,
                        "gateway_id": "1234ABCD1234",
                        "contents": [
                            {
                                "device_type": "Gateway",
                                "gateway_id": "1234ABCD1234"
                            },
                            {
                                "device_type": "Tenovi BPM - L",
                                "mac_address": "1A2B3C2A2B2C"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    ...
                ],
                "loose_items": []
            }
        ]
    }

